\f0\fs24 PublicLitigationOS \u8212? Local Harvest Runner (v2.0)\par
\par
This pack is a local-first harvesting + indexing runner for LitigationOS corpora.\par
It inventories court documents (PDF/DOCX/TXT/CSV/images), extracts text, OCRs image-only PDFs, and builds search indexes.\par
\par
Run (Windows): open PowerShell / Gemini CLI shell mode and execute: cmd /c RUN.cmd\par
Outputs are written to .out\\<RUN_ID>\\ including DASHBOARD.md and NEXT_PROMPT.md.\par
